    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Reference our TWX AJACI-1-2, 2nd Mar supplementary report follows:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "1. (A) At 2130 hours on 2nd Mar radar station picked up 2 objects 310 degrees, altitude 80000 feet, approximately 18 miles from Knoxville in general direction of Oak Ridge, moving in circular motion but in opposite directions.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "(B) At 2230 hours 2nd Mar and again at 0030 hours 3rd Mar station picked up object, moving same direction, locality and altitude.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "(C) Density of object similar to DC-3 airplane, speed not established but report as \"terrific\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "2. CIA Radar Technician reportedly arrives Knoxville today to check radar set and operation.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "3. Arrangement reportedly made by FBI with Naval and Marine Reserve Unit Knoxville to set up radar equipment to verify reception of WRQL radar station.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "4. All information on this subject this headquarters has been turned over to A-2 Fourteenth Air Force.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
